  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  COPD : FEV1/FVC &lt; 70%

          -  Smokers or ex-smokers ( ≥ 10 pack-years)

          -  No COPD exacerbation in the last three months

          -  No history of asthma and no respiratory allergy

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnant or nursing women

          -  Treatment with pulmonary vasodilators

          -  Patients with a significant acute disease. A significant disease is defined as a
             disease which, in the opinion of the investigator, may influence the results of the
             trial.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
